column5: Wow it is amazing what we take for granted daily , and its a true testament of human will. Great Video, very uplifting.
Ive seen that, and in this day and age...... impressed is an understatement
Very inspiring, makes the little problems we have seem trivial.

Man, what can you say? Wow comes to mind. I wasn't going to do what I was supposed to do today because I'm a bit sore, I'm heading out now because if he can do all that I can do a few very trivial chores. Inspirational to say the least.  Thanks Lew for the link.
If that doesn't inspire you nothing will. Thx for sharing that lew.
Side bar Lew. If they post a video of whatever McGyverism they have invented for him to do his "paperwork" in the bathroom...please don't post it on here
Thanks Lew...what a great way to start a day after seeing that. What an insperation!
